                                        <p class="mb-4 size-18">Earning your bachelor’s degree in Health Sciences at Marshall University in Huntington, West Virginia, will help you develop a strong foundation of core skills in preparation for a variety of health-related careers.</p>
                                  <h4 class="header-colorize">Why Study Health Sciences at Marshall?</h4>
