                                                          <p class="mb-4 size-18">Careers with a Sport Management degree will continue to grow in the coming years. Participation is expected to increase in organized and spectator sports to provide recreation and entertainment. Leisure sports for health-conscious Americans will also drive job growth. Future expansion of new professional sports teams and leagues, along with college athletic programs, will create more jobs in sport administration.<p>
                                                          <p class="mb-4 size-18">Earning your Bachelor of Science in Sport Management degree at Marshall University in Huntington, West Virginia, will enable you to develop the skills that meet the needs and demands of employers in the sport business sector.</p>
